      <div class="group bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hero-animate-delay-2 hover:border-secondary hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_var(--color-secondary)]" data-ps="src/components/about/Beliefs.astro:n2b38">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-secondary transition-all duration-300" data-ps="src/components/about/Beliefs.astro:4vahwn">Capital First Approach</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-muted leading-relaxed group-hover:text-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300" data-ps="src/components/about/Beliefs.astro:clu4v7">We believe in the power of focused capital. We rigorously identify high-potential businesses and supply the funding required to scale. Crucially, we leave the operational execution to the management teams, backing their proven expertise without imposing unsolicited advisory. This approach has enabled ease on both operator and investor's end.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Power of Wealth Generation -->
      <div class="group bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hero-animate-delay-3 hover:border-secondary hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_var(--color-secondary)]" data-ps="src/components/about/Beliefs.astro:c9v27">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-secondary transition-all duration-300" data-ps="src/components/about/Beliefs.astro:4vahwo">Power of Wealth Generation</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-muted leading-relaxed group-hover:text-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300" data-ps="src/components/about/Beliefs.astro:clu4v6">Our Group capital thesis revolves around long term compounding at both business and capital levels. We have explored that the best outcome is often achieved when we invest at a sapling stage and nurture it to become a strong tree bearing fruits of compounding.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Duty to our investor -->
